data.name: HelpBox.ToolTip
data.value:
The Seating Plan randomly distributes students among available desks.
The number of available desk spots increases with the size of this window.
Click on an empty spot to place a desk there. Click on an unoccupied desk to remove it. Once there are enough desks, you can click "Seat" to randomly seat all of the unseated students. The "Unseat" button will unseat all seated students.
You can click and drag students to empty desks, as well as to the unseated area.
